      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, scratches, or chips of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather seats show no signs of wear, all electronics function perfectly, and it still retains that new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no performance issues whatsoever. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on the finest days.",
