      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative vehicle, an exemplar of automotive excellence maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This unit exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. From its flawless exterior finish to its immaculate, factory-fresh interior, every detail has been preserved to the highest standard. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or professional to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
