    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and covered since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings to be found. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, wrapped in premium tires with nearly full tread depth. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition. The leather upholstery still possesses its original matte finish and factory scent, with zero wear on the seat bolsters or steering wheel. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, paper-documented service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. Recent preventative maintenance has been completed early to ensure total peace of mind for the next owner. This is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
